{"tid":555549,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"醒來變成北韓妹外傳：冬奥陰諜","createTime":"2018-02-09T14:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T17:31:26.000Z","uid":84696,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81fd97ffc7ee4627b3107849f95a0ffd808f8911","tid":555549,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\n睇平昌冬奥，又諗到個外傳<br />\n<br />\n之前正傳<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/130701/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/130701/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n序：冬奥陰諜<br />\n<br />\n我看着電視機上的平昌冬奥開幕式，今届香港的十六歲女生吳一里前往參加滑雪項目，希望<br />\n<br />\n她能為港爭光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己曾經是一名出色的運動員，不幸的是發生意外，雙腿要截肢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我試過多次自殺，現在正要服下一大瓶安眠藥，來世我要繼續做運動員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不久，藥力開始生效，我感到頭昏腦漲，漸漸失去意識......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不知死後的世界是如何，此刻看見耀眼的光芒，還夾雜喧鬧聲。身處奇怪的環境，全身起初<br />\n<br />\n都是動彈不得，但感覺到上身出現變化，血液流動加速，而失去雙腿的位置彷彿有生長的跡<br />\n<br />\n象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n持續了一會時間，我開始聽見清晰的韓文聲，嘗試掙扎身子，在用力睜開眼的一刻......<br />\n<br />\n「啊!」<br />\n<br />\n我大聲呼叫，身體恢復知覺，居然正在站立鏡子前，我長回雙腳了!?可奇怪的是......<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼我在說韓文?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鏡中身穿紅色大衣，頭戴黑色皮草帽的年輕美女是誰?是我!?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我雙腳一時不適應跌坐在地上，心想這是另一個人生開始......<br />\n<br />\n待續</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/221731_817db5698a41c99d871e3b3e80569ea6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F221731_817db5698a41c99d871e3b3e80569ea6.png&h=daec738c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/221731_02e1888f75e58f60398256d5ecdf2973.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F221731_02e1888f75e58f60398256d5ecdf2973.jpg&h=96db75e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不定期更新，希望多多Support，like share comment<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8E%8B%E5%A4%A9%E9%80%B8-298007653596115/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%2580%25B8-298007653596115%2F&d=j6WK1DOasCDWAJCd582MudWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=76addf48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8E%8B%E5%A4%A9%E9%80%B8-298007653596115/</a>"},{"pid":"57ac40ea4907b79785043edc33612076ad6b1e25","tid":555549,"uid":128748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"似曾相識喎巴打"},{"pid":"07b9fff9f689b83e8dc12312fc2dd4de8c0eff58","tid":555549,"uid":84696,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57ac40ea4907b79785043edc33612076ad6b1e25","tid":555549,"uid":128748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"似曾相識喎巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"無啦啦諗既外傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同主角"},{"pid":"86608552c50c8227d532d42762b085c29d560942","tid":555549,"uid":128748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"出文未"},{"pid":"a55bc2a9a00a983574bc3a334a2cb964cbcd156c","tid":555549,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86608552c50c8227d532d42762b085c29d560942","tid":555549,"uid":128748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"出文未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該聽晚正式開始<br />\n臨訓開左先"},{"pid":"9558a2e1dbdfb1656f1c81490b8124babf2ebf48","tid":555549,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T16:10:04.000Z","msg":"其實睇情況應該對哩個故唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都係算"},{"pid":"adf23b198a643f326b2c786ae1c845a44f4b8eab","tid":555549,"uid":15481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9558a2e1dbdfb1656f1c81490b8124babf2ebf48","tid":555549,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,